OL,3,CThe radical water fix: New regulator,
OL,4,Ccompulsory meters and higher bills
OL,6,FSir Jon Cunliffe's final report
OL,7,Fproposes a "reset" of the water
OL,8,Findustry - much like you might try to
OL,9,Frevive a glitch-riddled computer.
OL,11,FHe argues that the current system has
OL,12,Flost the trust of consumers,
OL,13,Fcompanies, and the investors we rely
OL,14,Fon to fund the response to more
OL,15,Fextreme weather, population growth,
OL,16,Fand the pollution of rivers and
OL,17,Fwaterways.
