OL,3,CThe radical water fix: New regulator,
OL,4,Ccompulsory meters and higher bills
OL,6,FThe 88 recommendations in his report
OL,7,Fare designed to restore that trust -
OL,8,Falbeit over a longer timescale than it
OL,9,Ftakes to reboot a laptop.
OL,11,FCunliffe's main recommendation is the
OL,12,Fcreation of a single, integrated water
OL,13,Fregulator.
OL,15,FIn England, Ofwat and the Drinking
OL,16,FWater Inspectorate would be replaced
OL,17,Fby a new body, which would also take
OL,18,Fon the water and environment-related
OL,19,Ffunctions of the Environment Agency
OL,20,Fand Natural England. In Wales, a
OL,21,Fsimilar body would be established.
