OL,3,CThe radical water fix: New regulator,
OL,4,Ccompulsory meters and higher bills
OL,6,FRegulation of the water companies
OL,7,Fwould become "supervisory" - similar
OL,8,Fto the way financial regulators
OL,9,Foversee banks (Cunliffe is a former
OL,10,Fdeputy governor of the Bank of
OL,11,FEngland).
OL,13,FEight new regional water system
OL,14,Fplanning authorities would be created
OL,15,Facross England and Wales to ensure
OL,16,Fthat the reservoirs and treatment
OL,17,Fcentres the UK needs actually get
OL,18,Fbuilt.
