OL,3,CThe radical water fix: New regulator,
OL,4,Ccompulsory meters and higher bills
OL,6,FThe report recommends giving it "the
OL,7,Fpower to block material changes in
OL,8,Fcontrol" and "to direct parent
OL,9,Fcompanies and ultimate controllers."
OL,11,FThese recommendations seem written
OL,12,Fwith one eye on Thames Water, which
OL,13,Fremains debt-laden and on the cusp of
OL,14,Fnationalisation.
OL,16,FCunliffe says he "understands" the
OL,17,Fpublic anger over bonuses paid to
OL,18,Fwater company executives, but believes
OL,19,Fthe backlash has gone too far.
