OL,3,CThe radical water fix: New regulator,
OL,4,Ccompulsory meters and higher bills
OL,6,FIn his view, bonuses can be a
OL,7,Flegitimate reward for strong
OL,8,Fperformance, but they should "drive
OL,9,Fthe right culture." He supports
OL,10,Fholding senior executives personally
OL,11,Faccountable for failure but thinks the
OL,12,Fcurrent regime should be "streamlined."
OL,14,FFixing the UK's water industry will
OL,15,Ftake time and money.
OL,17,FWater companies plan to spend #104
OL,18,Fbillion improving and maintaining
OL,19,Ftheir networks over the next five
OL,20,Fyears ` but they'll need to be able to
OL,21,Fborrow that money first.
